summary: Hey, you kids like the Spidered Man, right? That one webby fellow? Anyway, I know you’re busy playing Spider-Man’s great new PS4...
caption:
Hey, you kids like the Spidered Man, right? That one webby fellow?

Anyway, I know you’re busy playing Spider-Man’s great new PS4 game, but if you have a second to read this blog: it turns out that the next issue of the Fantastic Four, #218, is actually the second part of a story arc that begins in Peter Parker: The Spectacular Spider-Man #42! So we’ll be taking a look at that issue here before we plunge into that adventure.

Anyway, so here we go. It’s time to fight on top of the Statue of Liberty.
